Graffe’s Comprehensive Quad-Kiting Guide<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Compiled and Edited by: Shafli Tritium of Elder Fellowship (Povar)<br>
Submissions by: Many wise Sorcerers of Graffe, acknowledged on each entry.<br>
<br>
*NOT TO BE SHOWN TO DRUIDS UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTANCES*<br>
<br>
www.graffe.com<br>
www.elderfellowship.com<br>
