<br>
There are 2 wandering and 6 static on the island, go to the &quot;safe island&quot;, sit there.<br>
<br>
Sooner or later you'll be able to see both wanderers, just grab them, and the closest 2 static spawns, then only quad on that side of the island.  I wrapped them up over the water, ran straight back to the cliff base, snared, and quadded.<br>
<br>
That is the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>only</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> hard part.  Just med up, and there are 4 left on the island, quad using the whole island, and broken. Depending on mana/regen you should see them respawn sometime close to when you're very close to being ready for them <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showMessageRange?topicID=753.topic&start=21&stop=27>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=753.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=753.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.threadControl?topicID=753.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=753.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=753.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <b